    <h1>Emerson Electric (EMR)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Emerson Electric. — using FY2024 actuals, disclosed assumptions, and one final number.</p>
    <p class="date">Updated November 20, 2024 · Data: FY2024 10-K</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <!-- ═══ THE VERDICT ═══ -->
